The paper focuses on the parameterized approximability of the problem, which suggests that it is likely to belong to the sub-categories of algorithms and data structures (cs.DS), computational geometry (cs.CG), discrete mathematics (cs.DM), complexity theory (cs.CC), and game theory (cs.GT).
